WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.241
Familia ya majitu makubwa unayoifanyia kazi

00:00:10.241 --> 00:00:12.431
imeandaa karamu ya kuvutia,

00:00:12.431 --> 00:00:14.751
na wote wataka kuonekana 
wakiwa katika uzuri wao

00:00:14.751 --> 00:00:16.021
Lakini kuna tatizo moja -

00:00:16.021 --> 00:00:19.241
shati pendwa la kubwa la majitu 
limejikunja

00:00:19.241 --> 00:00:21.631
Kurekebisha, unatakiwa kuwasha...

00:00:21.631 --> 00:00:23.881
Pasi Kubwa.

00:00:23.881 --> 00:00:26.921
Pasi inahitaji betri mbili kubwa 
kufanya kazi.

00:00:26.921 --> 00:00:28.771
Ulikuwa na 4 tu zifanyazo kazi

00:00:28.771 --> 00:00:31.511
na 4 mbovu katika marundo tofauti.